updates.update_content:
Hello y'all, a very quick update to fill you in on my last month;

I burned out! Yeah...

I had a lot of momentum going into February, but somewhere I just hit the wall on a lot of my outstanding commitments, other comic work, and my motivation in general. Really disappointed in myself to be honest, but it let me breathe while I properly reorganized some of my life and knocked out smaller things that have been long neglected. Soon BULLISH will be my only real commitment and I'll have nothing else weighing on my mind, which is very good.
